HEADWORD: Frisker
<hw>Frisker</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who frisks; one
who leaps of dances in gayety; a wanton; an inconstant or unsettled
person.</def> <rj><au>Camden.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

